               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary><p>An incomplete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Tirukkuṟaḷ</title> ending with decade 86 (Ikal) in Poruṭpāl.</p>
<p>Contains decades 1-65, 67-79 twice, 80-86.</p>
<p>Appears to be a composite manuscript.</p>
<p>Description based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>         

                    </summary>
                  
